name: punycoder
desc:
Provides a Dart implementation of the Punycode encoding algorithm
specified in RFC 3492.

name: PunycodeCodec
desc: A codec for encoding and decoding strings using the Punycode algorithm.

name: PunycodeCodec.new
desc:
Creates a new instance of the Punycode codec designed
for working with domains and email addresses where
additional rules apply about how it is converted

name: PunycodeCodec.simple
desc:
Creates a new instance of the Punycode codec just designed
for working with simple strings

name: decoder
desc: Returns the decoder of this, converting from T to S.

name: encoder
desc: Returns the encoder from S to T.
